.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "Jan 6 2026" "1.0" "Simple Shell Manual"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- simple UNIX command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
simple_shell
.SH DESCRIPTION
simple_shell is a simple command line interpreter.
It displays a prompt and waits for a command.
It executes simple commands without arguments using fork and execve.
Only full paths to executables are supported.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0  if shell exits normally
1  if execve fails in child process
.SH EXAMPLES
$ ./simple_shell
$ /bin/ls
$ /bin/pwd
$ exit
.SH AUTHORS
